Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.35,0:00:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear the ultimate stage calling to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{op}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This voice! This melody!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be perfect for the final movement!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need more! Play more, Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is that energy coming from, Shrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's beautiful! Elegant and delicate, but strong and passionate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel its rhythm in my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.58,0:02:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never felt this way before!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shrade isn't wearing an Element suit. His body is effectively exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That means he can feel his surroundings keenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.21,0:02:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But it also means his body is taking more damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's seriously risking his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrade...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.24,0:02:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let my heart play its greatest cadenza!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.79,0:03:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I saw was real.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.49,0:03:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.72,0:03:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So of course I could never smell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You smell the same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This picture shows me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were originally one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.19,0:04:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata just watched as fate slipped away from him that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.67,0:04:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't gotten any better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata is a pathetic wimp who can't do a thing when it really counts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.78,0:04:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what about you? You never saved Mom either!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.67,0:04:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you been doing on Altair?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it across the dimensions, but I ended up losing Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.78,0:04:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage found me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, fragmented one. Dark Amata.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From this day on, you are now Kagura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:04:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had lost my memories. Mikage raised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about my mother anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea who or where she is, just like with my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one smell I care about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.53,0:05:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My own dear smelly wench, the real Silvie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not pathetic! And I won't let you have Mikono!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.47,0:05:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not good enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Why are you fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Stop fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Wings of the Sun are finally awakening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Amata?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.46,0:06:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say you're not pathetic? Prove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.55,0:07:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detecting higher-dimensional quanta!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.48,0:07:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're coming from near the former lake area!{??}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do these mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion is resonating with that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an ancient melody, coming to our ears from 12,000 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There can be no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.60,0:07:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the Legendary Aquarion from the myth!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At last!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.14,0:08:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At last you show yourself, Wings of the Sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.87,0:08:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's different...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono! Mikono!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you, Silvie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.19,0:08:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For 12,000 long years!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now I can finally kill you!{you know what this actually reminds me of? Dr. Forrester.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to kill Mikono!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.69,0:08:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bet I want to kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bitterly, violently, and coldly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.62,0:08:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to kill her over and over!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But first...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to crush you, Amata!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Silvie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.08,0:09:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get rid of him, and then we can kill each other all night long!{was "kill each other in the shallows" because it seriously sounds like "asaba de" but that makes no sense so fuck it, does Kagura have a cold?}{浅場で asaba de = in shallow water, I do not know what that is supposed to be the opposite of}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you touch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The higher-dimensional quantum emissions are still rising!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess that settles it. That's the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Legendary Aquarion?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stories are coming to life...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe we're actually here for this moment in history...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a momentous time, all right. So why is that kid messing around over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is another legend in itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.24,0:09:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,High Commander Fudo! When did you return?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.37,0:09:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You needn't concern yourself with this lovers' spat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't have her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.70,0:10:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was destined 12,000 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Silvie aren't fated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't fight fate, no matter how much you struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.84,0:10:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate even brought us together across the worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the wings to overcome fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your wings are useless if you can't fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.46,0:10:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, can you? Fly if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Don't hurt Amata anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate that smile of yours, Silvie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me want to kill you even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.39,0:11:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smile for me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.13,0:11:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More! Smile more!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{cm}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.18,0:11:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.23,0:11:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you're okay, Zessica!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.89,0:11:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too, Amata!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.61,0:11:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come back because you were worried about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.90,0:11:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zessica, I finally understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally know what's precious to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't die yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:11:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.69,0:12:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't fulfilled your promise to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noooooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.93,0:12:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't die yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you haven't fulfilled your promise to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.05,0:12:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.54,0:12:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see you two fight anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that, Mikono!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to settle this right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Settle what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.52,0:12:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want Mikono because you think you're destined?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly. How many times do I have to say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:13:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if Mikono is the reincarnation of Silvie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about whatever was fated 12,000 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love Mikono as she is right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono as she is right here, right now, this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's see which one's stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My destiny, or your burning emotions!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.61,0:13:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Wings of the Sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:14:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so close... I can almost hear the melody I've been searching for...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Shrade?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.31,0:14:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear it, my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that sound so beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrade's vital levels are dropping fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.23,0:14:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Further combat will put his life in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Element Change! Swap Shrade for Yunoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.36,0:14:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can still fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.90,0:14:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little more...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I almost...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Element Charge! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yunoha Thrul, entering battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Legendary Aquarion's higher-dimensional quantum emissions are beyond measurable bounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fudo, what is your goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.88,0:15:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't all this written in the Book of Genesis?{fuck it}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.83,0:15:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Legends can only be written by great and noble lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using spilled blood as ink.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't stop them, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no difference between moving and stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.87,0:16:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you clap your hands, what remains between them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.13,0:16:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. Just an empty void, a zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But zero is not always nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero is a value obtained by adding a positive and a negative together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.59,0:16:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is Mikono Suzushiro's power of connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark and light. Holy and profane. Good and evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Positive and negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let both their sealed memories be unlocked,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the infinite power of zero will be unleashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, a new page is turning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to my breast, Wings of the Sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.08,0:17:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He took the Legendary Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.83,0:17:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Gate's open. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both Abductors and the Legendary Aquarion have entered the Dimension Gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.14,0:18:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Chairman Crea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once more... let me go once more...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will die this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.72,0:18:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have known since you brought me to Neo-Deava.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.69,0:18:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That it would end this way someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just promise me one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you complete your song, let me hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both Vectors have entered the Dimension Gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've lost contact!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are Mikono and Kagura?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To complete the final song...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to take back the Legendary Aquarion first!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.28,0:19:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't take him on alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll Union with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zessica! You're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.31,0:20:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata... this is how I can show my love for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destiny Union! Go, Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.98,0:20:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.28,0:20:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Zessica.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My very soul is vibrating!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion Spada!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Legendary Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.01,0:20:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.66,0:20:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now repent your sins...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.28,0:20:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crucifixion Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dimension Gate is opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.29,0:21:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mithra Gnis is coming out on this side!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.10,0:21:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're detecting a Rare Igura in the cockpit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.71,0:21:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Rare Igura Kagura has been after all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She could well be the true Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.22,0:21:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare all units to sortie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.43,0:21:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot let Kagura take our true Eve for himself!{more like "keep her all to himself"}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.91,0:21:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have reports of crustal movement and abnormal weather all over the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.91,0:21:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The seal on the Legendary Aquarion has been lifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.36,0:22:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The balance between Vega and Altair it sustained is now shifting.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.04,0:22:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We lost the Legendary Aquarion, \nand we can't contact the Elements...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.87,0:22:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're helpless here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going to happen to the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.06,0:22:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is still hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.85,0:22:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Wings of the Sun will not move in the absence of its chosen Element.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.02,0:22:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.45,0:22:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to fulfill your promise, girl with hair the color of grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{ed}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.01,0:24:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you what I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.97,0:24:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colorful scattered flower petals
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.82,0:24:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Kagura's screams.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.16,0:24:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you what I hate, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.18,0:24:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Lies and betrayal...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.73,0:24:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}and him.
